伊维萨岛和巴利阿里群岛因野火发布红色警报，俱乐部成员发出警告https://www.nme.com/news/music/clubbers-warned-red-alert-issued-ibiza-and-balearic-islands-wildfires-3474759?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=clubbers-warned-red-alert-伊比沙岛和巴利阿里群岛发生野火Liberty DunworthFri, 28 Jul 2023 14:08:21 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3474759 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023 年，希腊埃维亚岛的森林发生野火" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>多地气温已达40℃以上</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/clubbers-warned-red-alert-issued-ibiza-and-balearic-islands-wildfires-3474759">伊比沙岛和巴利阿里群岛因山火发布红色警报，Clubbers 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023 年，希腊埃维亚岛的森林发生野火" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Europe-Wildfires-2023@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于高温和野火，俱乐部成员已被警告不要前往伊维萨岛和巴利阿里群岛。</p><p>极端天气条件影响了伊维萨岛、马略卡岛和梅诺卡岛等地区，部分地区气温升至 40°C 以上。</p><p>现在，巴利阿里群岛已经发布了“红色警报”，该地区的消防队员警告当地人和潜在游客，岛屿周围的树木繁茂的地区使他们变成了“易燃物”（来自<a href="https://mixmag.net/read/holiday-goers-warned-of-fire-risk-across-ibiza-majorca-and-menorca-news" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Mixmag</em></a> ）。</p><p>西班牙气象机构宣布，靠近热门度假胜地马盖鲁夫、帕尔马诺瓦和圣蓬萨的马略卡岛南端处于“极度戒备”状态，而东侧则面临着发生野火的“极高风险”。</p><p>伊维萨岛和梅诺卡岛已处于“高度戒备”状态，而由于担心山火可能迫在眉睫，居住在希腊科孚岛的人们已经收到疏散通知。</p><p>最近几周欧洲各地持续发生山火，过去几天有 19,000 人从希腊罗德岛撤离，随后发出了这些警告。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-66319340" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC 新闻</em></a>报道，希腊是目前正在努力应对山火的众多国家之一，迄今为止已有 40 多人因火灾死亡。 </p><figure id="attachment_3474764" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3474764" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3474764" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Wildfires-in-Greece-2023@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2023 年，希腊埃维亚岛加拉索纳村的野火熊熊燃烧" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Wildfires-in-Greece-2023@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Wildfires-in-Greece-2023@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Wildfires-in-Greece-2023@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Wildfires-in-Greece-2023@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Wildfires-in-Greece-2023@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Wildfires-in-Greece-2023@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3474764" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年，希腊埃维亚岛加拉索纳村的野火熊熊燃烧。图片来源：Alexandros Michailidis/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>意大利南部地区也受到严重影响，西西里岛和普利亚的火灾因土地干燥和大风而加剧。</p><p>在一项新的评估中，科学家们得出结论，人类行为引起的气候变化是造成令人震惊的热浪的主要原因，并确定这是一个“令人震惊的压倒性”因素（来自<a href="https://www.standard.co.uk/news/world/red-alert-fire-risk-majorca-menorca-ibiza-weather-b1096718.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《标准晚报》</em></a> ）。</p><p>这并不是近年来野火和极端天气条件第一次干扰欧洲各地即将举行的音乐活动。</p><p>去年，由于主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eddie-vedder">埃迪·维德（Eddie Vedder）</a>的喉咙因法国野火而受损<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pearl-jam-cancel-show-after-eddie-vedders-throat-is-damaged-by-dust-and-smoke-from-france-wildfires-3273794">，Pearl Jam 被迫取消了在维也纳的演出</a>。</p><p> “对于所有期待今晚在维也纳观看精彩珍珠果酱表演的人们，我们也是如此。然而，由于巴黎郊外最后一个户外场地的极端情况（高温、灰尘和火灾产生的烟雾），我们的歌手埃德·维德（Ed Vedder）的喉咙受伤了，”成员们当时<a href="https://twitter.com/PearlJam/status/1549803995509784579" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在推特上写道</a>。</p><p> “他已经看过医生并接受了治疗，但到目前为止，他的声带尚未恢复。对于所有相关人员来说，这是残酷的消息和可怕的时机。那些为演出而努力工作的人，以及那些付出宝贵时间和精力参加演出的人。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/clubbers-warned-red-alert-issued-ibiza-and-balearic-islands-wildfires-3474759">伊比沙岛和巴利阿里群岛因山火发布红色警报，Clubbers 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
